JIS_IDENTIFIER - Static variable in class tif.TagValueConverter
 
jpg - package jpg
Classes for parsing and manipulating JPEG-based files are found here.
JpgParser - Class in jpg
A parser for JPG image files that extracts metadata from the APP segments, handling multi-segment metadata, specifically for ICC and XMP data, in addition to the single-segment EXIF data.
JpgParser(String) - Constructor for class jpg.JpgParser
Constructs a new instance from a file path string.
JpgParser(Path) - Constructor for class jpg.JpgParser
Constructs a new instance with the specified file path.
JpgParser.JpgSegmentData - Class in jpg
A simple immutable data carrier for the raw byte arrays of the different metadata segments found in a JPEG file.
JpgSegmentConstants - Enum in jpg
This enumeration represents the known segment identifiers, that are often present in JPEG files.
JpgSegmentConstants(int, int, String, boolean) - Constructor for enum jpg.JpgSegmentConstants
 
JpgSegmentData(byte[], byte[], byte[]) - Constructor for class jpg.JpgParser.JpgSegmentData
